      "comment": "CAWBOURNE FOCUS (7) scored by 2.5 lengths last time (19.58) in a Free For All over 350m at this track. Yet to taste defeat in four runs from this draw. With a clean break looks hard to beat. VALEDICTORIAN (6) has a strong record here with two wins and a minor from three starts. In the money last time at this track (19.55) in a NG, finishing a 1.5 lengths second. Can feature in the finish. SCOTT WEDNESDAY (4) was prominent throughout when winning two back but could manage only midfield last time when 5th and beaten 7 lengths at Bulli (19.48). Can do much better this time. HARD STYLE CHICK (8) was in the money last start and likely to feature again.",
